ShortReasonCodes is a Field

    Representation
        AutoReasCd is an ApplicationAdjustmentReason
            occurs 3 times
	
	Local Fields
    	I1                is Numeric 2
              
    Field Rules
        ShortReasonCodes
            I1 = 1
            while (I1 <= 3)
                constraint (ShortReasonCodes.AutoReasCd[I1] != "CURR")
                    "CURRIsAReservedReasonCode"
                I1 += 1
	
